if(new URL(s).hostname!==new URL(this.targetOrigin).hostname||!l||l!=this.iframeid)return;
```
This confirms the hostname-only comparison.

### 2. Confirm `disableEmbeddedCSPEnforcement: true`
In the same file, find:
```javascript
kt=(e,t,a,s,o,l,n)=>({initConfig:_t(a,s,o,l,n),container:t,designerEnvironment:...production...,disableEmbeddedCSPEnforcement:!0,enableSandboxing:!0,...})
```
This confirms CSP enforcement is disabled in production.

### 3. Craft a PoC page (hosted at http://designer.microsoft.com or via MitM)
```html
