Any process running as the same macOS user account can:
1. Call `bootstrap_look_up("mach.streamrender.oophost.<id>")` to obtain a send right to the registered port (the service name suffix/identifier must be guessed or enumerated via `bootstrap_look_up` enumeration techniques).
