    "providers": {
      "vault": {
        "source": "exec",
        "command": "/usr/local/bin/op",
        "env": {
          "MY_SERVICE_KEY": "super-secret-credential-12345"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

**Step 2 – Call `config.get` on the gateway:**
```json
{"id":1,"method":"config.get","params":{}}
```

**Step 3 – Observe the response:**
The response will include:
